Line12.136591: Once you're in, hold their attention. Distract them however you can. I’ll be right on your heels.
Line7.136591: Here is how we’ll do this: show this insignia to the guard. Tell them you have an urgent message for their commander.
Line5.136591: He's an Inquisitor captain. A real zealot, can’t be reasoned with. I’ve tried.
Line1.136591: Damn it. This is Osric’s doing. The bastard has been stalking my every move.
VoiceDir7.136591: Explaining a detailed plan to the player so nothing is missed.
